      I really wanted to like these shoes, but they were a huge letdown. First, the comfort just isnt there. The cushioning is minimal, and after just a short run, my feet were soreespecially in the heel and arch. The midsole feels stiff and unforgiving, not what you want in a running shoe.

      The fit was also off. I ordered my usual size, but the toe box is narrow and cramped while the heel slips uncomfortably. The upper material looks durable, but it feels rough and stiff, almost like wearing plastic. Definitely not breathablemy feet felt overheated after only 20 minutes.

      After less than a month of casual use, the tread already started wearing down. For a shoe marketed for performance and running, the quality just isnt there.

      Would not recommend for serious runners or even casual walkers. There are much better options out there for the same priceor less.
